    "longBusinessSummary": "SEAREFICO Corporation operates in industrial refrigeration, and mechanical and electrical engineering sector in Vietnam. It manufactures and sells industrial refrigeration systems, smart cold storage systems, boilers, thermal equipment, quick-freezing equipment, food processing industry equipment, and post-harvest processing machines; and green building materials, such as PIR insulation panels. The company also engages in the design and construction of MEP and industrial construction; supply and installation of smart warehouses, technological lines, and automation systems in industrial plants; management, exploitation, M&A, and development of real estate projects; construction and installation of M&E systems, industrial refrigeration, manufacturing, exporting, processing, and manufacturing machinery, equipment, and accessories for the cold electromechanical industry; and consulting, designing, supplying, and installing construction equipment, maintenance, repair systems, and mechanical - thermal - refrigeration equipment for industrial and civil industries. In addition, it is involved in consulting, surveying, designing, and installing rooftop solar projects for industrial parks and residential homes; financial investment business; and supply and installation of automation systems for seafood processing, alcohol, beverage, etc. industries. The company also exports its products to Indonesia, the Philippines, Cambodia, India, and the South Pacific regions, including Solomon Islands. The company was founded in 1977 and is based in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
